    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers a straightforward opportunity for a value-focused buyer, commuter, or project enthusiast. It shows wear consistent with age and use, but presents as an affordable way to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget. If you\u2019re looking for practical transportation at an accessible price from a seller committed to clear, honest representation, this one is worth a look.",
