    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Reliable little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showroom car, but it starts, drives, and could be a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants affordable wheels, a simple project, or a handy spare vehicle. Priced to be approachable and sold with a friendly, straightforward sale.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Strong project or budget daily with a solid mechanical foundation and a drivetrain that still pulls cleanly. Starts, runs, and moves with usable power delivery, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup that appeals to DIY owners. Not perfect cosmetically and it shows age, but it presents as an honest driver with good parts value and plenty of life left for someone willing to sort the small stuff. Great candidate for a commuter, beater build, or weekend wrenching project.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap ride. Starts, moves, gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to sell fast. No fluff. Great beater or project.",
      "price": 4200.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built for the buyer who sees more than just a daily driver, this car has that honest, road-worn character that gives it real personality. It\u2019s the kind of vehicle that still turns every errand into a little adventure and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants affordable transportation with plenty of story left to write. If you appreciate charm, usefulness, and the chance to make something your own, this one is easy to root for.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
